    "As a result, any IoT-capable gadget may sense its surroundings, communicate, store, and analyze the data that it gathers, and take suitable action.",
    "All that occurs in the final stage of acting in the agreement is determined by the processing stage.",
    "An IoT service's actual level of intelligence can be determined by the amount of processing or action it is capable of.",
    "A non-smart IoT system will be unable to adapt to changing data and will have limited usefulness.",
    "Nevertheless, a more advanced IoT system will incorporate AI and may be able to achieve the actual objective of automation and adaptation."
